dct_title_s: Geologic map of the El Monte and Baldwin Park quadrangles, Los Angeles County, California
dct_alternative_sm: El Monte and Baldwin Park quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by Helmut E. Ehrenspeck; geologic cross sections researched and prepared by Wendy Lou Bartlett.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Prepared in cooperation with the California Dept. of Conservation, Division of Mines and Geology; and the U.S. Geological Survey."
Includes 3 col. cross-sections, and location map.
Duplicate legend, 3 cross sections, index to sources of geology, acknowledgements, map dedication, table of well information, and age correlation chart on verso.
dct_creator_sm: California, Division of Mines and Geology.
